      "writtenOn": "2016-04-27T19:28:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do we expect to be changing these at runtime or to sometimes not set them at all? If not, should they be part of the initRenderer call or a (probably protected) constructor that just stores these in this interface class (changing it from interface to abstract class)?",
