      "writtenOn": "2016-04-27T23:06:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "1. I doubt we\u0027re going to change them, but not setting them is totally possible.\n2. the constructor is a C function initLibrary(), I\u0027d just prefer to have it parameterless if possible",
