      "message": "+1 on that.\n\nAlso, as someone who\u0027s not familiar with the GL code, what does blocking do? My guess is it indicates if the read call should be blocking or not but could you add a comment to clarify that? I also think an enum would be a better choice than a bool here to increase readability.",
